# Didactic Resources
:res_alpaydin rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Introduction to Machine Learning" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "E. Alpaydin, MIT Press, 2004" .
:res_bishop rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Pattern Recognition and Machine Learning" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "C. Bishop" .
:res_cucker rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Learning Theory. An Approximation Theory Viewprint" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "F. Cucker and D. X. Zhou, Cambridge University Press, 2007" .
:res_deisenroth rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Mathematics for Machine Learning" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "M. P. Deisenroth et al., Cambridge University Press, 2020" .
:res_goodfellow rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Deep Learning" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "I. Goodfellow, W. Bengio and A. Courville, 2016" .
:res_haykin rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Neural Networks and Learning Machines" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "S. Haykin, Prentice Hall, 2008" .
:res_herbrich rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Learning Kernel Classifiers. Theory and algorithms" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "R. Herbrich, MIT Press, 2002" .
:res_james rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "An Introduction to Statistical Learning" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "G. James, D. Witten, T. Hastie, R. Tibshirani, Springer, 2014" .
:res_kohonen rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Self-Organizing Maps" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "T. Kohonen, Springer, 1995" .
:res_martin rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Aplicación de las redes neuronales artificiales a la regresión" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "Q. Martín, Y. de Paz, Cuadernos de Estadística, 2007" .
:res_mitchell rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Machine Learning" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "T. M. Mitchell, McGraw-Hill, 1997" .
:res_pearl rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Causal Inference in Statistics. A primer" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "J. Pearl et al., Wiley 2016" .
:res_vapnik rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Statistical Learning Theory" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "V. N. Vapnik, John Wiley & Sons, 1998" .
:res_vidyasagar_nonlinear rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Nonlinear Systems Analysis" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "M. Vidyasagar, Prentice-Hall, Inc., 1993" .
:res_vidyasagar_learning rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Learning and Generalisation" ; guide:bibliographyDescription "M. Vidyasagar, Springer, 2003" .

